  "statement": {
    "title": "NJT SDPA missing manual autocast for nested tensor inputs",
    "body": "When using `scaled_dot_product_attention` (SDPA) with nested tensors under autocast, the dtype is not correctly propagated, causing precision/dtype mismatches between the autocast cast and the operator inputs. The fix manually casts the nested tensor inputs to the autocast dtype.",
